---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Dixon Painting Co."
  description="Terms of service for Dixon Painting Co. — the terms governing use of our website and painting services."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="legal-hero__headline">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="legal-hero__sub">Last updated: April 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-content">
    <div class="container legal-content__inner">
      <div class="legal-prose">
        <h2>Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using the website at <strong>dixonpaintingco.com</strong>, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.</p>

        <h2>Use of the Website</h2>
        <p>This website is provided for informational purposes and to allow potential customers to contact Dixon Painting Co. for painting services. You agree to use the website only for lawful purposes and in a way that does not infringe on the rights of others.</p>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the site to transmit spam, malicious code, or unsolicited communications</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the site or its systems</li>
          <li>Use automated tools to scrape, crawl, or harvest data from the site</li>
          <li>Impersonate Dixon Painting Co. or any of its employees</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Estimate Requests</h2>
        <p>Submitting a form on our website is a request for a free, no-obligation estimate only. Submitting a form does not constitute an agreement for services, does not guarantee availability, and does not obligate either party to proceed with any project.</p>
        <p>All painting service agreements are separate from this website and governed by the written estimate and any service agreement provided at the time of booking.</p>

        <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>We make reasonable efforts to ensure the information on this website is accurate and up to date, including pricing guidance, service descriptions, and contact information. However, we do not warrant that any information on the site is complete, accurate, or current at all times.</p>
        <p>Actual pricing for any painting project will be provided via a written estimate after an on-site or virtual assessment.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website — including text, images, logos, and design — is the property of Dixon Painting Co. or its content providers and is protected by applicable copyright and intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use any content from this site without written permission.</p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Dixon Painting Co. is not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of this website or reliance on information provided on the site. Our total liability to you for any claim relating to this website shall not exceed the amount, if any, paid by you in connection with services booked through the site.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>This website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., Google Maps, social media). These links are provided for convenience only. Dixon Painting Co. is not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of any third-party sites.</p>

        <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

        <h2>Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California. Any disputes arising from these terms or your use of our website will be resolved in the courts of Solano County, California.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these Terms of Service, contact us:</p>
        <address class="legal-contact">
          <strong>Dixon Painting Co.</strong><br />
          Dixon, CA<br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:+19166122126" aria-label="Call Dixon Painting Co. at (916) 612-2126">(916) 612-2126</a>
        </address>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-hero { background: var(--color-primary); padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
  .legal-hero__headline { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-hero__sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.875rem; }

  .legal-content { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; background: #fff; }
  .legal-content__inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .legal-prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-prose p { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.975rem; }
  .legal-prose ul { margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .legal-prose li { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.65; font-size: 0.975rem; }
  .legal-prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-prose a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal-contact { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.975rem; }
</style>
